{"tid":735750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批美發動貿易戰自私　港團體遊行稱罷買美貨","createTime":"2018-07-09T17:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T20:15:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"21e900e7441cc65844fe22de637def3080197d2c","tid":735750,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"為抗議美國發動貿易戰，香港團體匯賢起動、同心護港、珍惜群組、反黑金反港獨關注組合共30餘人，今日(9日)由中環遮打花園遊行至美國駐港總領事館。他們撕毀印有美國總統特朗普頭像的紙張，批評他日前對中國加徵25%關稅，屬貿易霸凌主義，又高呼「不要貿易戰、不怕貿易戰」、「特朗普無事生非、經濟霸權更可悲」、「特朗普下台」等口號，強調會罷買美國貨，並將有關抗議交予領事館代表後和平散去。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/photo/bkn-20180709155751160-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180709155751160-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=23a4961c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bf275067f89ef38fb228b326c050ea2efd549f1","tid":735750,"uid":50182,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"件Nike 出賣咗個阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d9b5b281ab47adfc0b9d0285511744a0982ee2","tid":735750,"uid":2732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"又係5毛 又係廢老 玩完"},{"pid":"ecb4078c486d97dc383cff7baaeb7739ef7295d8","tid":735750,"uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"又係呢班垃圾<br />\n丟撚左自己部手機先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585af226c4d25013a5bfbed1f8c9ba53d27a7c4f","tid":735750,"uid":97739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bf275067f89ef38fb228b326c050ea2efd549f1","tid":735750,"uid":50182,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"件Nike 出賣咗個阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"可能之前買落呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/